    <item>
      <title>Control Structures</title>
      <link>https://kangifaz.com/docs/learn-python/fundamentals/control-structures/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:21:22 +0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://kangifaz.com/docs/learn-python/fundamentals/control-structures/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h3&gt;✅ Control Structures&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-control-structures&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-control-structures&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conditional statements (&lt;code&gt;if-else&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Loops (&lt;code&gt;for&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;while&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;List comprehensions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; range(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;):
